                     </persName>
                   thereto subscribed, and directed to Sir 
                     <persName id="t17950520-29-person363">
                        Richard
                         Glyn
                     <interp inst="t17950520-29-person363" type="surname" value="Glyn"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17950520-29-person363" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17950520-29-person363" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , Knt. and Co. of London, bankers, and partners, for the payment of twenty-two pounds, to Mr. S. Birch, or bearer, at sight; with intention to defraud <rs id="t17950520-29-viclabel166" type="occupation">Sir</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17950520-29-victim365 t17950520-29-viclabel166"></join> 
                  
                     
